        h3.text-blue App to app calling
        p Our Voice-over-IP (VoIP) platform offers crystal clear voice quality through High Definition audio codecs.
        ul
          li Improved user experience: design your own voice call UI to fit your app.
          li Increase app stickiness: users no longer need to leave your app when making a phone call.
          li Protect privacy: users can talk to each other without sharing phone numbers.
        p Video calling is coming soon. <a href="#subscribe-modal" ag-modal>Sign up to stay tuned</a>.

