        h3.text-blue Big Group Calls
        p If you need to talk to 2,000 people at once (e.g. a town hall meeting), Agora’s group calling is for you.
        p Big Group Calls is powered by Agora’s virtual network of 20+ globally distributed centers that intelligently route calls using a proprietary algorithm to ensure that all participants stay connected and enjoy a high quality voice call.
