        h3.text-blue Premium quality
        p Agora’s proprietary High Definition audio codecs preserves speech quality across various device, network, and background noise conditions. Transmitting audio across a super bandwidth, broader than Apple’s Facetime, Agora’s audio solution achieves unparalleled voice quality.
        p Agora’s state-of-the-art voice engine built on top of a global virtual network ensures call connectivity that many competitors are unable to achieve. Built on decades of experience, Agora’s proprietary technology eliminates adverse network conditions, from voice delays to dropped calls, by up to 70%.

    .row.feature-content.page-section
      .col-sm-8
        h3.text-blue Anonymous calling
        p Agora’s anonymous calling feature gives users peace of mind that their calls are private. This feature is especially popular in dating apps, where users can communicate with each other but can avoid revealing their name or phone numbers.
      .col-sm-3.hidden-xs
        .sprite-icon.anonymous-call-lg-icon

    .row.feature-content.page-section
      .col-sm-3.hidden-xs
        .sprite-icon.rocket-lg-icon
      .col-sm-8
        h3.text-blue Integrate in minutes
        p Agora’s simple SDK allows you to integrate call functionality into your app in just minutes. From documentation to integration, Agora’s Voice API is straightforward and built on simplicity. Adding a few lines of code opens up a limitless number of communication possibilities amongst your users.
        p Agora supports iOS, Android and Windows. We make adding calls from across different platforms and networks very quick and convenient. Agora supports secure, anonymous calling on all 3 platforms.
        p Want to integrate calling into your apps? <a href="#subscribe-modal" ag-modal>Get started with Agora today</a>!

